title: Shishman Mitsev
text: Shishman Mitsev (born 20 August 1937) is a Bulgarian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201960%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Welterweight">men's welterweight</a> event at the <a href="1960%20Summer%20Olympics">1960 Summer Olympics</a>.
